Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: surveillance outside containment and/or protection zone; surveillance within containment and/or protection zone; official disposal of carcasses, by-products and waste; control of wildlife reservoirs; zoning; vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists); no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: no other measures

